{"tid":2358552,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港而家仲有冇街頭小食？","createTime":"2021-01-08T08:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T19:49:43.000Z","uid":309049,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d970e0f0f9a28fc3464e076a2b832cb8eb513b6","tid":2358552,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"我去台灣，韓國玩，都會有d夜市，步行街之類，一檔檔小食攤，可以一路慢慢行一路食一路睇下鋪頭咁，我可以一條街食好多唔同地道小食。<br />\n<br />\n香港除左葵廣，我諗唔起有類似室外步行街，係街邊想食串魚蛋買餅雞蛋仔，而家已經好難，行好耐搵到一檔，都冇地方可以舒服咁食。<br />\n<br />\n而家如果遊客問我香港有咩街頭小食，我都好難介紹，心諗搵間7仔食魚蛋燒賣可能仲好。"},{"pid":"76160853db26cc7d675bfac602c3027838e4e779","tid":2358552,"uid":117894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"見到你夠唔夠膽食姐？<br />\n例如觀塘檔車仔牛雜"},{"pid":"46b8b6fbcf765c2b250a6abb1ff6c68b6f49d997","tid":2358552,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"厚福街?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab054b7993349549cba4954f6a563c910c5c1f45","tid":2358552,"uid":182789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"尚德好似有夜市"},{"pid":"0631c9f19b769535cd2299fd150f78346a568f3a","tid":2358552,"uid":13361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"南山村？太安樓？"},{"pid":"b383974ef28957ca57444f6c26a7bd2a544a6d85","tid":2358552,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0631c9f19b769535cd2299fd150f78346a568f3a","tid":2358552,"uid":13361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"南山村？太安樓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"南山村好少喎<br />\n而且唔係好有連續性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15765b5418a44330c3bba34c1f93b568a5e55239","tid":2358552,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T19:43:11.000Z","msg":"香港小食唔夠創意就真 來來去去都嗰d"},{"pid":"f581a1551091cfe7f5